FEDERAL EXPENDITURES FUND $5,836,454 $18,107,487 $19,275,103
TOTAL
FEDERAL BLOCK GRANT FUND 2024-25 2025-26 2026-27
All Other $181,750 $563,875 $600,235
__________ __________ __________
FEDERAL BLOCK GRANT FUND $181,750 $563,875 $600,235
TOTAL
Mental Health Services - Community Z198
Initiative: Deappropriates one-time funding provided under Public Law 2023, chapter 643,
Part A for the start-up and implementation costs of mental health organizations
participating in certified community behavioral health clinic projects previously funded by
federal grants from the United States Department of Health and Human Services, Substance
Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration.
